    <source>Cooper B.F. et al.: Benchmarking Cloud Serving Systems with YCSB, ACM SoCC 2010, doi:10.1145/1807128.1807152</source>
    <methodology>Doc 32 Lastprofil-Katalog (33-Paper-Analyse); op-mix/dist auf uint64-Op-Modell gemappt</methodology>
